definitions.definition: A person who occupies an office or a position .
examples: I cannot say the same of the current occupant of the position

definitions.definition: A person who occupies a place.

subdefinitions.definition: A person sitting in a car or other vehicle.

definitions.definition: The owner or tenant of a property .
